title: 10: How To Stop Procrastinating
description:
Have you ever put off something urgent but unpleasant in favor of more pleasurable tasks? We've all been victims of the super-villain of procrastination...but we don't have to be. In this episode, I share my tips on booting procrastination from your life.

 

Join Our Kwik Brain Facebook Community: www.kwikbrain.com

 

Don't Forget, Subscribe & Review.
